id=adguardhome
name=AdGuard Home (DNS ad-blocker)
version=v1.0.3
versionCode=4
author=kaandikec
description=Network-wide DNS ad-blocker for rooted Android (ZTE F50). Runs AdGuard Home daemon on port 5353; hotspot clients are transparently redirected via iptables NAT (inserted at PREROUTING position 1, beats ZTE firmware's DNAT-to-1.1.1.1). Web UI at http://192.168.0.1:3000 from any connected client. Self-updates via the statusbot /update command. Requires bin-utils v1.3.0+.
updateJson=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dikeckaan/magisk-zte-f50-adguardhome/main/update.json
